    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Castle Daybreak</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Castle Daybreak is an indie single-player class-based Action RPG; set in a medieval world on the verge of being overrun by an unrelenting evil.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock powerful and unique abilities for your class! Mix and match Perks and weapons to build the perfect build while climbing through the levels and defeating all the enemies that stand in your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714100/extras/d5bfc8bd00226fb6ede468729648bddd.poster.avif?t=1727823120\" width=672 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714100/extras/d5bfc8bd00226fb6ede468729648bddd.webm?t=1727823120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714100/extras/d5bfc8bd00226fb6ede468729648bddd.mp4?t=1727823120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Class-Based</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose one of five unique classes to start your adventure, each with their own unique set of abilities. Play as the <strong>Rogue</strong>, an agile fighter that can quickly dart around the battlefield in an instant. The <strong>Guardian</strong> brings the heat with destructive AOE abilities and charming little fox for companionship. The <strong>Duelist</strong> lives for melee combat and specializes in up close and personal conflict resolution. The <strong>Vanguard</strong> has a wide assortment of abilities, most of which focuses on de-buffing the enemy and staying alive. The <strong>Healer</strong>, possessing an understanding of healing and medicine, also comprehends the techniques of virulence. The <strong>Exalted</strong> is the sixth class that is only available after completing a specific achievement in game. This class prioritizes using numerous companions alongside mind-controlling abilities to decimate their foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714100/extras/3a980634d839b7813449758dbe4ed87c.poster.avif?t=1727823120\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714100/extras/3a980634d839b7813449758dbe4ed87c.webm?t=1727823120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714100/extras/3a980634d839b7813449758dbe4ed87c.mp4?t=1727823120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Open World</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the Island of Victoris, a once prosperous island that was destroyed by greed and corruption, shortly followed by a catastrophic event that left the island forever changed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and grow your power by capturing enemy fortifications, participating in random events scattered through most of the island. Delve into dungeons and reclaim epic loot that will aide in battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714100/extras/15c3e2f04a242e4325327c6327efb394.poster.avif?t=1727823120\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714100/extras/15c3e2f04a242e4325327c6327efb394.webm?t=1727823120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714100/extras/15c3e2f04a242e4325327c6327efb394.mp4?t=1727823120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Instanced Dungeons</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dungeons are a great way to level up and find new gear and weapons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714100/extras/270b62451a30bde625526f66fe931516.poster.avif?t=1727823120\" width=776 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714100/extras/270b62451a30bde625526f66fe931516.webm?t=1727823120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714100/extras/270b62451a30bde625526f66fe931516.mp4?t=1727823120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
